  <Subject Subject_ID="300006366">
    <Parent_Relationships>
      <Preferred_Parent>
        <Parent_Subject_ID>300120461</Parent_Subject_ID>
        <Relationship_Type>Parent/Child</Relationship_Type>
        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>power plant buildings (utilities buildings) [300120461], utilities buildings [300165470], industrial buildings [300006231], industrial structures [300121918], single built works by function [300004894], single built works by specific type [300004795], single built works (built environment) [300004790], Single Built Works (hierarchy name) [300004789], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
      </Preferred_Parent>
    </Parent_Relationships>
    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Buildings in which electricity or other forms of power are generated for the operation of machinery or vehicles, or supplying power to other buildings in a complex. Dstinguished from "power plants" which are larger complexes producing power on a much larger scale for a community, and which can include a "power plant building" on the premises.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Edificio en el que se genera electricidad u otras formas de energía para el funcionamiento de las maquinarias, los vehículos, o para suministrar energía a otros edificios en un complejo. Distíngase de de las "plantas eléctricas", que son complejos en los que se produce energía a una escala mucho mayor.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Te gebruiken voor gebouwen waar elektriciteit en andere vormen van energie worden opgewekt voor het aandrijven van machines of voertuigen, of om stroom te leveren aan andere gebouwen in een complex; te onderscheiden van 'elektriciteitscentrales' die energie leveren op veel grotere schaal.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>產生電力或其他形式之動力，以供應機械或運載工具運轉的建築物，或供應複合建築中其他建築物所需之動力；和「發電廠」有所區分，後者指大規模產生電力的複合建築。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
